name: Kubye Clicker
description:
Click Kubye West to get POINTS! Get 20,000 points to WIN!

This was a project made from a joke among the boys called "Kubye West". Kubye West is an EPIC cube form of Kanye West. He can morph into school food, memorize the lyrics for the Eat Pant Anthem, AND MUCH MORE!

PLEASE CONSIDER DONATING!
